{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"d6f3bf92-365a-430d-a319-b01dbd958cc8","content":"In **MSTest.Sdk 3.8.0**, `Microsoft.Testing.Platform` is the default runner. You just need to:\n\n1. **Remove** (or set to `false`) the `<UseVSTest>` property in your project file:\n   ```xml\n   <!-- Delete this line -->\n   <UseVSTest>true</UseVSTest>\n   ```\n\n2. **Update your test invocation** — `dotnet test` continues to work, but you can also run the test executable directly for the new platform's CLI:\n   ```bash\n   dotnet test            # still works\n   dotnet run --project MyTests  # direct runner\n   ```\n\n3. **Review any VSTest-specific settings:**\n   - `.runsettings` files are still supported but some adapters/extensions may need their Microsoft.Testing.Platform equivalents.\n   - If you use `[DataRow]`, `[DynamicData]`, etc., those work unchanged.\n   - Custom VSTest loggers (e.g., `--logger trx`) become `--report-trx` (install `Microsoft.Testing.Extensions.TrxReport` if needed).\n\n**No other package changes are required** — `MSTest.Sdk` already bundles the correct references.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"3bd36861-e1e0-4465-a1b3-bdc5635020ed","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about migrating from VSTest to Microsoft.Testing.Platform in their MSTest project. This is a knowledge-based question about .NET testing configuration. Let me provide a concise answer based on my knowledge.\n\nWith MSTest.Sdk/3.8.0, switching from VSTest to Microsoft.Testing.Platform is straightforward:\n\n1. Remove `<UseVSTest>true</UseVSTest>` from your project file (or set it to `false`)\n2. That's it - MSTest.Sdk 3.8.0 defaults to Microsoft.Testing.Platform when `UseVSTest` is not set to `true`\n\n\n3. I should also note that this change affects how you run tests from the CLI - you'll use the standard dotnet test command which now routes through Microsoft.Testing.Platform instead of VSTest.","outputTokens":467,"requestId":"7C19:175BE3:263309B:2A43037:69F93F9F"},"id":"d32f4ac9-ba55-4685-8794-ef8523eb32f7","timestamp":"2026-05-05T00:54:01.932Z","parentId":"4857972e-e267-44ba-866e-7e9f9bee2e35"}
